snippet.title: PopStop TV
snippet.description:
PopStopTV.com is your ultimate one-stop-shop for breaking pop culture news around the globe! PopStop TV provides viewers with a behind-the-scenes look at what's hot in young Hollywood and connects celebrities to their fans by interacting with LIVE audience feed via Twitter, Facebook, Google +, and other social media platforms.

Check out http://www.PopStopTV.com
Follow us on Twitter @PopStopTV #PopStopTV

You can watch PopStop TV on your TV! Tune in to Channel 64 Direct/Dish/AT&T, Channel 20 Fios, and Channel 32 Time Warner. Check your local listings.
If you're in UK/Ireland, watch PopStop TV every day on Sky TV Channel 292.
